casebody.data:
No. 1201,

Mise.

Collier v. Wingo, Warden.

C. A. 6th Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Harlan would grant certiorari, vacate the judgment below, and remand for the reasons stated in his separate opinion in Chambers v. Maroney, ante, p. 55. Mr. Justice Marshall would grant certiorari, vacate the judgment, and remand for further consideration in the light of Chambers v. Maroney, ante, p. 42.
